Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Otake High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel! Where is he going like that? \NA blooming flagrancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, a greeting for a transferred student...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be such idiot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy sure is nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:01:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I kick your ass? \N(Shibai Taroka)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't believe he can get Okajima.\NI'd rather bet he drops dead on the first shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But this Yakuda is also a real deal.\NSuch tough face should cover an according character.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be be experienced, \Nbut so is Okajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In this school, such arrogance \Nwill ruin him, just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We should find out, which one is stronger? \NSo far, Yakuda sure wins a face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Pansy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, lads, bloom and prosper, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:33.26,Song,,0,0,0,,Daigo Yakuda, 16 yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda, here you are, finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the five ones, \Ntrampled by your classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Kariya from the C-class wants to speak to you, \Nthey're waiting for you behind the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't speak to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't go, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return this to the washroom instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He totally doesn't look like a 16 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta go to the washroom anyway now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with Kariya myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, you have to believe me! \NI was just persuaded to call you in, nothing aside that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the gymnasium?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I got transferred just recently. \NI don't know where the gymnasium yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not be as bad as his face appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who called me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was rude, my flowers got trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:48.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Kariya Masataka, 16yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard, you weren't too sweet \Non my friend being polite either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by face, he has already lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For no reason, you hit our man \Nand didn't say a word afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For no reason?{\i0} Did this bastard \Nreally tell you I had no reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love flowers, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He pretends to like flowers? \NThen bastard will have it for his funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's how it is. \NBy the way, what's with your laces?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a quick victory. \NWon't even have to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a barbarian!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Students at this school have no respect \Nnor love for flowers in their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like they were already taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else but the gardening club teacher \Ndoes it on holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.24,Song,,0,0,0,,Manami Sera, 16yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else but the teacher \Nspares time for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing does not belong to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! \NI'm the only one to hold this school in my fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kariya Masataka. For today, \NI forgive you due to being a transferred newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, \NI won't let you get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, Kariya! \NStop it! Stop, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on it again, Kariya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuckin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:38.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Miyama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, teacher. \NDon't you want to let go of me already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a friendly bros' conversation.\NDidn't you see yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariya! Fighting is strictly prohibited! \NFor how long are you planning to keep it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting? You must be joking. We were just \Nkickinspecting one another's martial arts styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fond of inspecting things.\NIt makes me burn with enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just inspecting one another's martial arts. \NRight, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Being enthusiastic about research is great, \Nbut you still should be reasonable, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, I remember sudden blow, \Nlike if something hit Okajima's valet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta think something bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hooey! \NThis could not be the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose! \NI just stumbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he want? \NHe isn't gonna beat me up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely fine. \NIt didn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't try to molest a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But he had his tooth knocked out. \NI don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock-knock on wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy, if you look up at him, \Nreminds me of my father, I wonder how old is he.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to talk to Sera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky! \NIn addition...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To such a reason for happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a scratch, nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was he? The guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our students?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,High school students are almost adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want something \Nfrom that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You naughty boy! \NNot in such place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go any further, \NI'm afraid I won't be able to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't. \NSomeone might come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what can I do if it's love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear something now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it was of pain or of joy, \NI heard a woman's cry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard a thing. \NYou must have misheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? \NSo be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more important, \Nis it true what they say happened earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened earlier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda was beaten to the pulp like never before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This one? True indeed. By the guy who claimed \Nto love flowers despite his most unfitting for it face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soliloquy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was him who beat Okajima. \NHe was the only one able to tame Yakuda's iron fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite having a face like this, \Nhe isn't a bad person at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be thinking of me quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's just a cold... \NI wouldn't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy! Sorry to bother, \Nbut won't you mind fetching this to the teachers' room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher forgot something at home you see, \Nneed to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have something to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's step away for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How about later? The teacher asked me to bring \Nsomething to the teachers' room, I don't have "bits."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear what I said previously? \NI can repeat it for you if you didn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us settle it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I couldn't get this guy over with quickly, \Nthus he has made himself Okajima's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I'm not some demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like carrying out the group lynching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you fair, \Nlike the unaware of anything transfer student you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say you don't want to become my cugine, \NI think I'll be fine with letting you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, a wise choice should I notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be a reasonable man \Nand a "don't judge a book by its cover" instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Also tell this guy, \Nhe owes 10000 yen for the flowers ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See now? \NRegardless of face, he still pees his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People are never what they appear to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if it COincides he COmes to us later, \Nhe'd COllect a few new bumps, right, Kariya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, what on the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So womanly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I take a canned coffee for you, Kariya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I also want a melon bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's a shortcut to the way out, \Nsuch is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a reason to trample the beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How can be those guys be so ruthless?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a deplorable situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even mind where are you walking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall telling you I love flowers already. \NDon't you still get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy smacks them all up! \NSo easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were serious about loving flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you claimed to love flowers \Nonly as a mean to avoid the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the guy who loves to watch the Sakura blossom. \NI like it too! Such is my character!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me? \NI never noticed you exhibit such a liking, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Teachers' Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers were delivered safe and sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.88,Song,,0,0,0,,To teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's still too early to rejoice. \NThings can't go smooth with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.92,Song,,0,0,0,,To teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for making me deliver the flowers \Nwith a constant expectation of something fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What will he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A little advice on flowers:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, you expose them \Nto a bit too much water and sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Saintpaulia is vulnerable to the direct sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,From Yakuda Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If it won't bother you, \Ndo you mind sharing one sprout with me later?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard what they say \Nabout our recent transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer student... \NYou mean that year 1 class B Yakuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right! They say, right this morning, \Nhe knocked out 10 of our students all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we had \Nsome outstanding transfer this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even we, teaching staff, no matter how old he is, \Nshould be feared of a child like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I ended up \Nasking the favour of a thug!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She has such a fine body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, we'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn it... \NI can't hold myself any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kariya...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would class C Kariya come all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at, morons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, I'm also this class' student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best in studies, Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi! I expect you all to take care of me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter? \NHas something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My, it's class C Kariya here. \NWhat for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're to warm up now, \Nhow about some soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you a silver-haired man's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? \NI have no idea of such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It means little to me without a name. \NCall him by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a piece of cloth torn out here. \NTake it off. This should be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hurts your feelings, just shove them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't rely on the parents only.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the fuck are you going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And what're you looking at, dimwits!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain, at this time, the year 1 class B is having \Nthe physical education. Or is it in a cold season?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that, things are getting overcomplicated! \NMaybe, I should see the doctor for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This Yakuda bastard made a sweet face at first \Nbut uprose against you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit about the cloth hole was a fucking lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, he tries his best \Nto mock and disgrace Kariya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to scare Kariya-san away. \NBut he's just the sucker who hits from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Things can be settled not through fight alone. \NOnly a man of many talents can be a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also well known that at war \Nthe safety is in numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on we're also gonna be rising in numbers. \NIt's always better to have some warriors guarding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it also must be the allegiant warriors, \Ncommitted to me from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But this jackass Yakuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He is who he is. \NBut he'll become a guy to die for my prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him love flowers all he wants. \NHe is but an ugly weirdo now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His fighting skills are more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:18:03.71,Song,,0,0,0,,The Story of Great Pure Love
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really helped me out this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. This is the one you wanted \Nto borrow from me, Saintpaulia flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I left that notice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardening teacher and Yakuda \Ntalk horticulture stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda is moving right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he accidentally grabbed some green along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seen this money? It must have been \Na token of appreciation for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardening teacher bribed him with this money, \Nno doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The bodyguards also require a fee, \Nespecially the ones looking yakuza-like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.79,Song,,0,0,0,,Teachers' Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the teachers here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your money anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.18,Song,,0,0,0,,10,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Thank you, Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda, weren't you the one \Nwho protected the flowerbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, when it got trampled, \Nyou bothered to fix and water it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kind, aren't you, Yakuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The flowers always make me feel better. \NI just need to be gentle to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, when I'm stressed, \Ntheir beauty relieves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A gospel truth! \NTurns out, Yakuda, despite the face, you can be romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I said it doesn't suit your face, \Nshould've kept that to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know \Nwhat's got into me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NWhy do Sera hangs out around this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? \NIt's because Sera is a gardening club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be very brave to do so! \NTalking to such guy with a complete composure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! \NI've read a book about something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember Yakuda is bodyguarding that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He started doing it \Nas a mean to approach Sera easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His aim is Sera's voluptuous body only!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The bust is 85, the waist is 56, hips - 83!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? \NYou know Sera's three sizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They say girls these days prefer exceptional guys. \NWhat if he starts dating her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yakuda exceptional?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He even ribboned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Sera knows what Saintpaulia \Nstands for in the flowers' language.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I better write or say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock... \NSera-san with such a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cheer up, will ya? \NIsn't it time we go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hang out here any longer, \Nthe watchman drives us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing? \NThe after-school activities time is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for my friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and head home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NHas someone yelled now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saburo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.31,Song,,0,0,0,,Gymnasium storeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone there? Hey! \NWhat on Earth happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NDoes it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, not so fast, mongrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do to her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What else? \NI was surprised to notice a mouse in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing aside that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He also assaults women now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And of all people he picked Sera-san! \NUnforgivable! Absolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera has? \NWait, Yakuda beat her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday after-school \Nin the gymnasium storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrifying!\NWhat will happen to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher rushed there at once, \Nbut didn't make it in time to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! \NAbsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know, \Nwho was running near the gymnasium yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you bright and early?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody seems to have any idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I clearly saw you doing it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You approach us and start accusing guys \Nthough they know nothing. Don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. \NNo idea what're you talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not Yakuda's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply heard my cry \Nand came to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NIt was pitch dark and I couldn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened so abruptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it wasn't Yakuda, \Ncan you explain why he was watching you sob?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NSo fearsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, I already said you have nothing to fear. \NSo, Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In any way, it was totally not Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I forgot it already. \NLet's not speak about it anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.07,0:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys could not hold on even for a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,His strength is transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's even the deal with you all? \NHe disposed of you 10 times easier than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.42,0:24:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.22,0:24:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about. \NI replanted them to another place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:25:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand still, I'll check your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.73,0:25:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This Yakuda is doing something to her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.77,0:25:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.84,0:25:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he trying to make her kiss him forcibly?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.21,0:25:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was actually evil all the way \Nbut I couldn't tell the truth beforehand! Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.51,0:25:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Manami \Nwill be pumped and dumped, tattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he is done with Manami's body, \Nhe'll come for mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.52,0:25:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be totally safe, you hear me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.22,0:25:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.66,0:25:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice I stepped on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.40,0:25:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.03,0:25:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? \NIs your eye better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.40,0:25:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda's eyedrops did me great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.37,0:25:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He made Sera cry too!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a cute pouch you have here! \NDid someone gift it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my appearance, \Nwomen always consider me a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned to care for myself \Nno worse than a woman would.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In contrast, you are kind, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.40,0:26:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall you had a brawl with Kariya the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.04,0:26:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He may look arrogant, \Nbut in reality he is a good boy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.05,0:26:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, do you mind getting along with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.02,0:26:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, if you look closely on it, \Nyou have a pretty refined face!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.96,0:26:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.20,0:26:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, lil' sis, lil' sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.83,0:26:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sis!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.87,0:26:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.57,0:26:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! This Yakuda is a jerk! \NWe just need a small handicap against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:27:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Just look at it, Okajima! \NYakuda and doctor Miyama are cooing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.92,0:27:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.72,0:27:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just chattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.52,0:27:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Say nothing, \Nlet me do just one bang, and we're over."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.26,0:27:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right after all! \NWhere is he going to bang her I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.33,0:27:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the women, \Nhe decided to lay his hands on Kariya's woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.27,0:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With this guy, \Nit just keeps getting better!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You sure we should let Kariya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.67,0:27:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm at that, track down those two, \Nand I'll make sure to amuse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.98,0:27:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.78,0:27:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You were more gentle at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.35,0:27:43.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Infirmary
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.49,0:27:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a swift bastard! \NThey have already started.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.90,0:27:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.54,0:27:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda! It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.47,0:27:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.07,0:28:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Deeper!\N- They really are doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.18,0:28:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Miyama and Yakuda do sex!? \NAre you fucking sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.05,0:28:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No room for doubt. Doctor Miyama \Nwas moaning with such pleasure there...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda, fucker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.76,0:28:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Yakuda. \NYou're so good at massage!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to it, \Nmy back pain has gone into thin air!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.03,0:28:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an anma massage pro. \NThe neighbouring old lady often had back problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.90,0:28:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask you to ever come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.81,0:28:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I can take care of you anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.51,0:28:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole... He seized the preemptive punch chance, \Nmeans I'll mince him with particular cruelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.13,0:28:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What imbecile would leave \Na block weighing ton in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.37,0:29:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I will do it now! \NI have to do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.90,0:29:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have no next chance to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.39,0:29:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give way, give way!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.89,0:29:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.39,0:29:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys? \NCan't they show some discipline in a campus at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.06,0:29:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What if those guys are Kariya's cugines, \Navenging him being smashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.86,0:29:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they up to then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.73,0:29:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual way! \NThey probably seek to group lynch Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.90,0:29:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't such litigation means cowardice?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.11,0:29:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For a Yakuza like Yakuda, serves him right. \NFight fire with fire they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.15,0:29:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He had me unconscious. \NYakuda, you bastard, not this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.60,0:29:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy Yakuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.86,0:30:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he begs for mercy sobbingly, it's too late. \NI already have a mind to show him a true fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.97,0:30:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, with this guy's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.80,0:30:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,his crying face would resemble \Nan infant punished for misbehaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.66,0:30:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That sonofabitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.60,0:30:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm growing tired of all this fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.10,0:30:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even received 2 to 3 punches this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.64,0:30:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad for the skin as delicate as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.95,0:30:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where my first aid kit comes in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.38,0:30:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I apply my favourite \Ncharacter Band-Aid, it'd be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.94,0:31:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your petty revolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.11,0:31:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I put you down for good, Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.45,0:31:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Men should care for each other's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.99,0:31:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.56,0:31:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no reason to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.73,0:31:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a treacherous man, Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.17,0:31:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.37,0:31:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case I will encounter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.28,0:31:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Clingy jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.62,0:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you got me ignited.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.85,0:32:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? I can't hear from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.12,0:32:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.49,0:32:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn bastard... Die, will ya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.80,0:32:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.21,0:32:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an emergency, Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.65,0:32:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice putt!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.45,0:32:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible situation is taking place!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.35,0:32:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is taking place, gardening teacher? \NPlease, get yourself together and explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.86,0:32:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice-principal, I didn't know you are also here. \NBut that's even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.66,0:32:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment ago, at the schoolyard, \NKariya and the transferred Yakuda
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.23,0:32:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,have started a serious brawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.97,0:33:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Means that rogue Kariya and the Mobster Face \Nfinally get people's attention, so we could transfer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.64,0:33:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What a happy-go-lucky approach!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.74,0:33:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is it? \NIs the fight in Kariya's favour?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.45,0:33:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather say it's an even battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This only grows more entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.62,0:33:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see lively students in our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.22,0:33:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, the conflict is not resolved \Nuntil one of the parties is knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.76,0:33:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The battles can also be wholesome! \NIsn't it one of the citizenship education doctrines?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.66,0:33:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Those boys are versed in fighting, \Ntrading punches until one's death is not about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.44,0:33:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, for the worst-case scenario, we have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.11,0:33:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce. I invited this discipline \Nenforcer here as our insurance for the next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.91,0:33:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Nishinari.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.22,0:33:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher Nishinari has the 4th Dan in Judo \Nand the 8th Dan in Karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.26,0:33:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,During his college days, an amateur wrestling champion. \NTruly, a man of valour.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.43,0:34:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, none of our children would be able to brush us off by pulling a grimace like they used to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.44,0:34:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.84,0:34:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.67,0:34:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.71,0:35:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't know - perhaps, in Osaka you were the top gun, \Nbut here I'm the only top gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.15,0:35:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have to say just one thing. \NYou are quite tough, lil' bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.55,0:35:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kariya! \NDon't you dare to call me brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can consider it a boast, \Nbut you can't defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will ya ever shut up, jackass!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.11,0:35:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.08,0:35:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giving up{\i0} already? \NGuys like you are always all mouth and no trousers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, just a temporary armistice. \NTake a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.16,0:36:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Need a reconstruction to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.44,0:36:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda and Kariya, \Nyou shouldn't fight any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.84,0:36:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera! Step away! Run! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.48,0:36:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.70,0:36:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.73,0:36:52.37,Song,,0,0,0,,Notice board: Year 1 class C - Kariya Masataka expelled. \NYear 1 class B - Daigo Yakuda, suspended for an indefinite period.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.72,0:36:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We succeeded no matter what. Everything \Nwas resolved smoothly and the most pleasant way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Delinquents' chief is rid of. "Block Reconstructor to go on" \Nis also successfully made away with.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.65,0:37:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks to teacher Nishinari, \Nthe campus is also subdued quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.39,0:37:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,More than ever, our institution \Nis a perfect fee-paying school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.79,0:37:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.99,0:37:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trampling the flowerbeds, \Neveryone is trying to win Nishinari's favour now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.86,0:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is just splendid! Because if it goes on, \Nwe may apply for funding soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.50,0:37:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, this funding \Nought to be of a significant kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.67,0:37:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A ratio no lower than of rivals'.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.28,0:37:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now! What's going on? \NYou aren't one of our students anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.18,0:37:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.12,0:37:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!\NYou are but pigs wearing a fake loving smile skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.02,0:37:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you step into trouble, \NI suggest you retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.96,0:37:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal's new watchdog can fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.93,0:37:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NWith such punches, you won't even hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.65,0:38:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NOut of breath already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.98,0:38:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to punch, \Nthen hit like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.76,0:38:19.93,Song,,0,0,0,,Girl's friends
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? They got Kariya done?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.36,0:38:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariya was hospitalized with his right leg broken. \NWe have no one else to rely on, but you, Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.47,0:38:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kariya himself admitted so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.11,0:38:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if someone tells me to, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.51,0:38:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera? Has your injury healed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.01,0:38:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What's more important, Yakuda, \Ndo your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.18,0:38:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.58,0:38:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They impute you with crushing \Nthe gardening club flowerbeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.75,0:38:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, \Nyou should visit the principal and explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.39,0:38:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear it from Ryota?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.13,0:38:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:38:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Yakuda turned out \Nto be precisely the kind of man that I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.53,0:39:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And which, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.67,0:39:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,May I try to clarify? Yakuda surely is one manly fellow, \Nin the sense that he is a kind-hearted justice devotee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.37,0:39:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The manliest man of all men! An ideal type for Sera, \Nor so they say... That was a little redundant...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.55,0:39:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had plenty of time \Nto learn to watch your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.42,0:39:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you go watch me through the window then. \NCause I will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.66,0:39:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And whoever gets in my way \Nwill be whipped 'till the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.26,0:39:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to bear a martyr role...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.77,0:39:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But does such simple-mindedness \Nreally attracts women?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.17,0:39:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go, go, Yakuda! \NGo, go, Yakuda! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.21,0:39:45.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Principal's
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.21,0:39:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! \NYou can't enter without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Learn to knock! To knock... \N- Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Was not suspending me as a "Block Reconstructor \Nto go on" enough for punishments?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:40:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NLeave the office please!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.09,0:40:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have deceived common folk, \Nbut I'm a deceiver myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.23,0:40:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're knee-deep in hassle, \Nbullish and with a pitch-black soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.20,0:40:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boss treated you like the precious flower earlier. \NGo home before he regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.57,0:40:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To him, I am no other essence \Nthan King Kong himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though my friends admire my modesty, \NI might as well hit back damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your petty revenge is not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.49,0:40:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.65,0:40:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious sake is wasted!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.42,0:41:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.77,0:41:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.20,0:41:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.35,0:41:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This big mouth guy is sure a roly-poly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.03,0:41:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.13,0:41:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.45,0:41:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.57,0:41:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, your feeble strength \Nbelongs to the nursing home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.11,0:41:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.34,0:41:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While my real strength \Nwas not yet exposed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.15,0:42:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Finishing blow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.76,0:42:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this? Is the taste of my righteous \Nfull-power fist thrust to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.34,0:42:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So-so, it at least resembles a gun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.34,0:42:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.62,0:42:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.67,0:43:04.34,Song,,0,0,0,,Notice board: former principal Honda (rogue), \Nformer vice-principal Sakurai (bandit) (thief) \Nboth dishonourably discharged for self-enrichment on behalf of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.34,0:43:08.92,Song,,0,0,0,,Year 1 class B Daigo Yakuda, \Nyear 1 class C Kariya Masataka, \Nboth aforementioned reinstated in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.35,0:43:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our best flowering in my whole life. \NWhat a joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.19,0:43:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gardening teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.39,0:43:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly am happy about this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.66,0:43:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The commemorative photo is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.77,0:43:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda is not present?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.23,0:43:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll go fetch him. \N- No, you should be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.18,0:43:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.58,0:43:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't refuse even if everyone finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.75,0:43:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No refusing. \NI love you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.06,0:43:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda! \NBut in such a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.33,0:43:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,His sleeping face is so cute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.13,0:44:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, what kind of dream \Nyou might be seeing, Yakuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.65,0:44:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What, 'tis but a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.95,0:44:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate, \Nit felt so real...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the white snake is a good omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.45,0:44:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be of a prophetic dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.83,0:44:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It somehow made me want to take a piss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.94,0:44:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The restroom is afar, \Nmaybe do it right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.59,0:44:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.13,0:45:05.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Otake High School
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.31,0:45:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.01,0:45:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, what's going on? Yakuda right now \Nwas trying to strangle Manami with a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.22,0:45:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But soon as I noticed, he fled this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.12,0:45:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful walking alone. \NThis time he retreated only because I came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.89,0:45:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. \NI know Yakuda couldn't have been doing it, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.06,0:45:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't, Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.53,0:45:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda! Are you here? \NHe isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.27,0:45:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have escaped through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.30,0:45:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu must have misunderstood. \NYakuda is really not a bad person at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.94,0:45:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so, \NI can't trust this man after what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.28,0:45:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fine. \NWith time, you'll grow believing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.18,0:46:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, how was it? \NYou Sunday date.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.02,0:46:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun. \NI never regretted going.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.32,0:46:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll make a fine couple! \NYou both know to give and take.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.06,0:46:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But well, so far I've been taking only.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.36,0:46:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I also had no chance to give yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.06,0:46:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I get you since our three sizes are almost the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.37,0:46:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.50,0:46:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Date, huh? \NI'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.37,0:46:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.31,0:46:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitomi and Keiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.24,0:46:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Ijima over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.61,0:46:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, aren't you afraid \Nof getting too close with Ijima?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.51,0:46:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.88,0:46:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.25,0:46:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows that girl is dating yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.92,0:46:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He acts quiet towards Ijima only. \NAnd it seems she is fooled by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.66,0:46:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are worried \Nthat you might follow the similar model.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.27,0:46:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, don't fall for the same bluff. \NYakuza are always what they look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.61,0:46:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.14,0:47:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Today you told Sera you're virtually her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.21,0:47:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That you two have nearly the same sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.05,0:47:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have just a small favour to ask, so please listen. \NI need to take measurements of the sister's body sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to my woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.47,0:47:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy? \NAre we doubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.41,0:47:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He acts quiet towards Ijima only. \NAnd it seems she is fooled by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.11,0:47:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.75,0:47:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure have some guts. \NCourting a yakuza's woman with a peacock look.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.55,0:47:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If willing to play with a schoolgirl, \Nyou should get Ministry of Education approval first, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.43,0:47:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuzas don't give a shit about it, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.40,0:47:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrogant brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.94,0:48:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.78,0:48:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.06,0:48:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, so what do you think about my offer? \N- NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.97,0:48:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey, come on. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.25,0:48:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do now? \NFainted before I could do any explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.12,0:48:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, at least I can peacefully \Ntake measurements of the sizes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.43,0:48:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.05,0:48:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you abuse her, bastard, \NI swear, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.86,0:48:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.63,0:49:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.47,0:49:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong. \NI'm just assessing her body sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.74,0:49:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My beloved woman have sizes similar to your woman's, \Nand I was planning to gift her a sweater, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.04,0:49:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no coercion in mind, \Nbut she didn't listen when I said so straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.81,0:49:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Pops, I don't want a burden \Nof being branded selfish by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.52,0:49:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,One's imagination is often deceptive. \NYou should know by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.85,0:49:23.32,Song,,0,0,0,,2 months later
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.89,0:49:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He also told me \Nhe quit the gang he belonged to before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.96,0:49:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Being defeated by Yakuda, \Nhe saw he should change his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.06,0:49:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda fought him too?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.76,0:49:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight a yakuza, he surely has to be one big stubborn, \Nnot knowing when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.64,0:49:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he fought fiercely. \NYour class is lucky to have such a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.81,0:49:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But losing to a high school student \Nmust have been a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.41,0:49:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more will they walk together? \NI can't give her my knitted sweater in front of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.85,0:49:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakuda was just trying \Nto protect her from a yakuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.98,0:49:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't know. \NMaybe he planned to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.35,0:49:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a charming sweater!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.69,0:49:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.09,0:50:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna buy it? Manami, didn't you say \Nyou want a sweater of that kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.66,0:50:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's adorable, \NI already have 4 white sweaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.93,0:50:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely wanted a different colour this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.60,0:50:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The sweater that Yak-kun was kneading \Npast the last 2 months was white, precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.78,0:50:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.75,0:50:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You are exactly the one I needed now. \NGot a small favour to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.73,0:50:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem with this sweater. \NI assume such never happened before,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.13,0:50:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but can you present it to your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.06,0:50:41.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Several days later
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.60,0:50:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My! What a lovely sweater!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.44,0:50:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A present from boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.80,0:50:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice! \NWhen you don't wear it, may I lend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.47,0:50:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Manami greatly fancied \Nthe sweater knitted by Yakuda after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.35,0:50:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Angel remained deaf \Nto Yak-kun's pleas.
